data.description: Don't miss this 5 bedroom, 3.5 bath home with formal dinning room, family room, eat in kitchen with a breakfast bar and a walk-out basement with patio! The living room is open to the kitchen area boasting a fireplace for cozy evenings. The kitchen accesses the rear deck with steps to the back yard!!! The upper level boast the large primary bedroom with a walk-in closet, master bath that has a double vanity sink, stand up shower and a jetted garden tub!!!! There are 3 additional large bedrooms all on the upper level along with a 2nd full bath! The lower level offers a huge 5th bedroom with private bath.  PLUS a family room with access to the lower patio!! The home also includes a huge storage shed as a added bonus for mower and lawn equipment storage! 15 Minutes from Ft Knox, 25 Minutes to the New Blue Oval Ford Plant, 30 minute to the Louisville International Airport. Seller offering 3k painting allowance
